display_long_description:
Dive into the immersive world of Project Chimp New Seed, a gaming experience where reality and horror seamlessly collide. Whether you're seeking spine-chilling thrills with friends or a more relaxed setting, Project Chimp New Seed offers a unique blend of terror and camaraderie.

Embark on nerve-wracking adventures with friends, navigating through spine-tingling environments filled with twists and turns. Confront fears together, relying on teamwork to unravel mysteries. From dark tunnels with monsters to dirt mazes, each map is crafted for heart-pounding experiences.

Rooms:
1. Space Area: 
2. Basement (Spawn): Initial spawning point.
3. Forest: (The area up the pipe)
4. Shop (Checkered Area): The store where you can get cosmetics
5. Fan Art (Room with all the paintings): An area where fan art of the game is put up
6. Parkour (Red Room): Self explained

Game Modes:
- Casual: Just a area to hang out.
- Horror: The main game mode.

Project Chimp New Seed seamlessly blends social interaction with horror elements, catering to all preferences. Whether you're a horror enthusiast or seeking a virtual space to unwind with friends, Project Chimp New Seed promises an unparalleled fusion of social engagement and thrilling gameplay. Are you ready to face your fears and create unforgettable memories in the world of Project Chimp New Seed?
